title: Boards Profile
body: Does this happen with anyone else? Is it just rito not updating league of legends? I am confused. I also cannot seem to upvote or comment on anything but i assume that's actually supposed to happen? In case for some reason you're not seeing the page i'm seeing, It appears to be an old boards page.

replies.body: This usually happens when posting for the first time or your profile needs to sync.  Your post here helped, but you can also use this[ syncing too.](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool)

https://drive.google.com/open?id=1aDVmjUYuPyV8StxYd5R9UNP0ZlGCnqj2

This is a screenshot of what happened before hand. I couldn't post or upvote anything for a while because of it. So i feel its funny the problem automagically fixed itself
Upon posting this the problem quite literally solved itself. I guess i needed a history or something.
